<inglise> - or to have all their produce in respect of which recognition has been accorded marketed by the group or union respectively, either in the name and on behalf of the members, or on behalf of the members, or in the name and on behalf of the group or union. </inglise>
<eesti> - lasta kogu oma tunnustatud toodang turustada r&uuml;hmal v&otilde;i liidul kas liikmete nimel ja huvides v&otilde;i liikmete huvides v&otilde;i r&uuml;hma v&otilde;i liidu nimel ja huvides. </eesti>
<inglise> As far as producer groups are concerned, this obligation shall not apply to products: </inglise>
