<inglise> - for which the producers had concluded sales contracts or granted options before joining the group, provided that the group was informed before those producers joined of the extent and duration of the obligations thus contracted and has approved them; </inglise>
<eesti> - mille kohta tootjad on s&otilde;lminud m&uuml;&uuml;gilepingud v&otilde;i ostuees&otilde;iguse enne r&uuml;hmaga &uuml;hinemist, tingimusel, et r&uuml;hma teavitati enne tootjate &uuml;hinemist lepinguj&auml;rgsete kohustuste ulatusest ja kestusest ning r&uuml;hm on need heaks kiitnud; </eesti>
